      <span>Description</span>
    </div>
    <div class="infoDrawer_tab_item">
      <span>Shipping</span>
    </div>
    <div class="infoDrawer_tab_item">
      <span>in the box</span>
    </div>
    <div class="infoDrawer_tab_item">
      <span>Fit guide</span>
    </div>
    <div class="infoDrawer_tab_item">
      <span>Material</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="infoDrawer_description">
    <p>
      The Zero-G Plus Clear visor is built for athletes who play hard and demand the best on the field. Originally
      designed for the Riddell Speedflex, it’s confirmed to fit all current football helmets, including the Riddell
      Axiom (top-bar facemask) and the Schutt F7 Pro and F7 Air. Trusted by tens of thousands of players for clarity,
      protection, and performance.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
      .infoDrawer_tab_wrapper{
